Simple ncgi web and gopher imageboard.

Requirements: tcllib (ncgi, term), sqlite3 (with tcl support)

Scripts:

get.tcl -- Pulls images out of list stored in urls.txt. requires wget.

categorize.tcl -- Categorizes retrieved images, scales thumbnails and adds titles. Requires feh, imagemagic.

web.tcl -- ngci web backend for the board.

eek.dcgi -- dcgi (geomyidae) backend for the board.

rss.cgi, rsslib.tcl, rss.tcl -- ngci rss backend for the board.